- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper deals with a swarm of particles, which can be considered as a multi-agent system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper provides algorithms for collecting the swarm, which involves decision-making and planning, falling under the domain of AI.
